-run the chosen code via comand promt (Linus: shell, Windows: CMD or powershell)  
-first you type how many operator enlargements you want to have (on RaspberryPi zero: 1000)  
-second you type the number of how many times the test should run  
  
Note: every test creates an .txt files with the used time for each operator increment (for 10 test you get 10 files)
